import './Blast.css' import axios from 'axios' import { useForm } from 'react-hook-form' import {useEffect, useState} from 'react' const Blast = () => { const {register, handleSubmit} = useForm() const [databases, getDatabases] = useState() const getBlastDb = () => { axios.get(`http://192.168.1.37:8080/db/blast-db`).then(res => { getDatabases(res.data.map(entry => { return })) }) } useEffect(getBlastDb, []) const sendRequest = (data, service) => { let form = new FormData() Object.keys(data).map(key => { if(key==="files")Object.keys(data.files).map(file => form.append("file", data.files[file])) else form.append(key, data[key]) console.log(key) console.log({key: data[key]}) }) console.log(form.getAll()) axios.post(`http://192.168.1.37:8080/services/${service}`, form, { headers: { "Content-type":"multipart/form-data" } }) .then() .catch() } return (
sendRequest(data,'blast')) }>
) } export default Blast
